<i>such a handsome city</i>

01:19.611 --> 01:21.812
<i>in so much scaffolding.</i>

01:26.278 --> 01:29.211
<i>There wasn't always this much</i>
<i>scaffolding in New York.</i>

01:29.278 --> 01:31.044
-♪ (PIANO MUSIC PLAYING) ♪
