02:37.812 --> 02:39.678
<i>whether the building needs it</i>
<i>or not.</i>

02:40.845 --> 02:42.978
<i>This turned</i>
<i>New York City scaffolding</i>

02:43.044 --> 02:46.044
<i>into an eight-billion-dollar-</i>
<i>a-year industry.</i>

02:46.111 --> 02:49.144
<i>And it doesn't seem like</i>
<i>it's gonna be slowing down</i>

02:49.211 --> 02:50.478
<i>anytime soon.</i>

02:50.545 --> 02:53.078
