<i>Every crew has a--</i>
<i>a "hammer guy," uh, just one.</i>

04:49.078 --> 04:52.345
<i>Or sometimes two.</i>
<i>Two hammer guys.</i>

04:52.411 --> 04:55.878
<i>Uh, the "roll-dog" drives</i>
<i>the crew between job sites.</i>

04:57.044 --> 04:59.611
<i>The "bathroom attendant"</i>
<i>gives them a--</i>

05:00.211 --> 05:01.411
<i>a pot to piss in.</i>

05:02.645 --> 05:06.578
<i>The "sweetman" cools them down</i>
<i>at the end of a long afternoon.</i>

05:06.645 --> 05:09.845
<i>And Spot here, uh,</i>
