<i>is only meant to be temporary,</i>

05:25.078 --> 05:29.011
<i>the people who put it up</i>
<i>usually don't care how it looks.</i>

05:29.078 --> 05:31.578
<i>At best, the design</i>
<i>of most scaffolding</i>

05:31.645 --> 05:33.411
<i>is aggressively neutral.</i>

05:33.478 --> 05:34.945
<i>But a lot of people see this</i>

05:35.011 --> 05:37.912
