<i>which makes it feel</i>
<i>like you're waltzing</i>

05:46.311 --> 05:49.278
<i>through some kind</i>
<i>of Italian villa.</i>

05:49.345 --> 05:51.845
♪ (MANDOLIN MUSIC PLAYING) ♪

05:53.411 --> 05:55.712
-♪ (FLUTE MUSIC PLAYING) ♪
-JOHN: <i>And it seems like</i>
<i>across the city,</i>

