<i>There are a lot</i>
<i>of iconic buildings</i>

09:40.345 --> 09:43.945
<i>that show up all the time</i>
<i>in movies about New York City.</i>

09:44.011 --> 09:45.978
<i>There's usually never anything</i>
<i>obstructing them</i>

09:46.044 --> 09:49.411
<i>in the establishing shots,</i>
<i>but in reality,</i>

09:49.478 --> 09:51.545
<i>all of these buildings</i>
<i>are usually covered</i>

09:51.611 --> 09:53.411
